7月11日，之前对飓风比尔移动方向构成影响的锋面系统在[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]近海催生出不具备热带天气系统特征的低气压。随着锋面系统逐渐消散，低气压持续了一段时间基本没有移动，再于7月13日在北卡罗莱纳州[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]东南偏南方向约523公里海域发展成第三号热带低气压。根据[[侦察机|侦察机]]的数据，气象部门认定系统迅速增强成热带风暴克劳德特。风暴向东北方向前进，从[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]东南方向经过。虽然受到风切变的不利影响，但气旋还是发展出[[雨带|带状特征]]。7月14日，克劳德特达到风力时速72公里的最高强度，然后因受锋面系统影响转向东进。<ref name="ctcr">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997claudett.html | title = Tropical Storm Claudette Preliminary Report | author = Edward N. Rappaport | date = 1997-08-13 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221050908/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997claudett.html | accessdate = 2015-06-06 | format = HTML | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-21 }}</ref>

风暴关联的雷暴活动相对混乱且零散，克劳德特也在7月16日减弱成热带低气压。气旋这天再度达到热带风暴强度，但很快就于当晚转变成温带气旋。此后不久，系统与冷锋融合，其残留于7月23日在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]附近失去踪影。<ref name="ctcr" />热带风暴克劳德特对陆地的影响很小<ref name="Daily">{{cite news | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Hz8PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=HIYDAAAAIBAJ&dq=tropical+storm+claudette+1997&pg=5167,4086003&hl=en | agency = Reuters | title = Tropical Storm Claudette pushes north | date = 1997-07-14 | newspaper = Daily News | accessdate = 2015-06-06 | archive-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201213232912/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Hz8PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=HIYDAAAAIBAJ&dq=tropical+storm+claudette+1997&pg=5167%2C4086003&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，北卡罗莱纳州出现强烈的离岸流，多人需要救援，有1人受伤，但没有人员遇难<ref name="stormdata">{{cite report | url = http://maestro.srcc.lsu.edu/softlib/sd/sd9707.pdf | archivedate = 2006-03-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060330011935/http://maestro.srcc.lsu.edu/softlib/sd/sd9707.pdf | title = Storm Data And Unusual Weather Phenomena With Late Reports And Corrections | author = Stephen Del Greco | date = 1997-07 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2006-03-30 | format = PDF | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。北卡罗莱纳州沿海地区部分居民甚至对风暴一直停留在海上感到失望，因为他们期望风暴能带来雨水，缓解当地旱情<ref name="Vigrinian-pilot">{{cite news | title = Claudette- and all her rain – expected to remain out to sea | author = Steve Stone | date = 1997-07-15 | newspaper = The Virginian-Pilot Archives | accessdate = 2015-06-06 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=VP&p_theme=vp&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAFFAC45AFF19E9&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-11-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201126030430/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=VP&p_theme=vp&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAFFAC45AFF19E9&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
